            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1665139010447-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, cut your<strong> lettuce </strong>into quarters lengthways, then give them a wash and pat dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Chop your <strong>chives </strong>finely</p><p>Slice your <strong>cheddar cheese</strong> into 3 slices per person</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1665139020813-x200.jpg",
