          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1665139020813-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Line a separate baking tray with <strong>tin foil</strong></p><p>Add your <strong>ultimate vegan burger patties</strong> to one side of the lined tray and put in the oven for 10-12 min or until cooked through</p>",
      "order": 3,
