      "instruction": "<p>Once the patties are cooked through, remove the tray from the oven and top the <strong>ultimate vegan burger patties</strong> with the <strong>cheese slices</strong></p><p>Slice your <strong>ciabatta[s]</strong> in half and add them to the other side of the tray</p><p>Return the tray[s] to the oven for 3-4 min or until the cheese has melted and the ciabattas are toasted</p>",
